data.description: Imagine living in this stunning home with 4 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms, flooded with natural light through its expansive big windows. You'll relish the luxury of a large primary bedroom complete with an ensuite bathroom, providing a space to retreat and recharge. You'll also have ample room for entertaining in the spacious formal dining room and living room on the main floor, accentuated by a cozy fireplace. The kitchen boasts plenty of space, including a charming breakfast nook to enjoy your morning coffee. Plus, forget about HOA fees causing unnecessary expenses. The walkout basement with a fireplace and abundant storage space is perfect for creating a cozy additional living area or accommodating all your belongings. Lastly, the huge backyard will provide endless possibilities for outdoor activities and relaxation. Don't miss out on this captivating home that has everything you've been dreaming of and more.
